========================================================================
                      ENTITY-RELATIONSHIP (ER) DIAGRAM
                     Floral E-Commerce Website - Florish
========================================================================

ASCII Mapping of Entities, Keys, and Relational Cardinality:

     +------------------+                    +------------------+
     |       USER       |                    |     WISHLIST     |
     +------------------+                    +------------------+
     | PK  _id          |<------------------1| FK  user         |
     |     name         |                    |     products[]   |
     |     email (UK)   |                    +------------------+
     |     password     |
     |     role         |
     +------------------+
              |
              | 1
              |
              | 1..*
     +------------------+                    +------------------+
     |      ORDER       |                    |       CART       |
     +------------------+                    +------------------+
     | PK  _id          |<------------------1| FK  user         |
     | FK  user         |                    |     items[]      |
     |     items[]      |                    +------------------+
     |     address      |                              |
     |     totalPrice   |                              |
     |     status       |                              |
     +------------------+                              |
              |                                        |
              |                                        |
              | *                                      | *
              +----------------- REFERENCES -----------+
                                     |
                                     V
                           +------------------+
                           |     PRODUCT      |
                           +------------------+
                           | PK  _id          |
                           |     sku (UK)     |
                           |     name (UK)    |
                           |     price        |
                           |     stock        |
                           +------------------+
                                     ^
                                     | 1
                                     |
                                     | *
                           +------------------+
                           |      REVIEW      |
                           +------------------+
                           | PK  _id          |
                           | FK  product      |
                           | FK  user         |
                           |     rating       |
                           +------------------+

------------------------------------------------------------------------
Cardinality Key:
- User to Cart: 1-to-1 (Each user has one persistent shopping cart)
- User to Wishlist: 1-to-1 (Each user has one wishlist)
- User to Order: 1-to-Many (Each user can place multiple orders)
- Product to Review: 1-to-Many (Each product can have multiple reviews)
========================================================================
